text: OMG the worst experience just now w @UPSHelp. I have a package thats been sitting in their Shrewsbury MA location for 24 hrs. I asked if I could come and pick it up tomorrow. The person on the phone gave me a pick location in Montana. REALLY? Zero satisfaction.

@saxdan I can see you are upset, and understandably so! Please DM us with the tracking number, address, and your contact phone number. We can look into this for you to see what can be done to help resolve the matter. ^WS https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
